---
import Layout from "../components/Layout.astro";
import Heading from "../components/Heading.astro";
---

<Layout title="关于 — G400 技术笔记" description="关于我和这个博客">
  <script slot="head" type="application/ld+json" set:html={JSON.stringify({
    "@context": "https://schema.org",
    "@type": "AboutPage",
    "name": "关于 G400 技术笔记",
    "description": "关于我和这个博客",
    "url": Astro.site?.href + "about/",
    "mainEntity": {
      "@type": "Person",
      "name": "G400",
      "url": Astro.site?.href,
    },
  })} />

  <article class="prose">
    <Heading as="h1">关于</Heading>

    <p>之所以本博客叫 G400，是因为我用的笔记本型号是联想的 G400。</p>

    <p>而这台笔记本是父亲送我的。</p>

    <p>感谢父亲。</p>

    <h2>联系我</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>GitHub: <a href="https://github.com/dadadaqiang">dadadaqiang</a></li>
    </ul>
  </article>
</Layout>
